OL,3,CMan escaped psychiatric unit before
OL,4,Ckilling 'beloved' churchwarden
OL,6,FWatch the moment of David Parish's
OL,7,Farrest
OL,9,FA 38-year-old man has been handed a
OL,10,Fsix-year custodial sentence after
OL,11,Fadmitting to killing a churchwarden
OL,12,Fwith an umbrella in Somerset in March
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FDavid Parish pleaded guilty in January
OL,16,Fto the manslaughter of Beryl Purdy by
OL,17,Fdiminished responsibility, and
OL,18,Fappeared at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,19,FFriday 23 May for his sentencing.
