OL,3,CMan escaped psychiatric unit before
OL,4,Ckilling 'beloved' churchwarden
OL,6,FThe court was told Parish attacked the
OL,7,F86-year-old in her home after
OL,8,Fabsconding from a mental health unit
OL,9,Fearlier the same day.
OL,11,FThe churchwarden's family described it
OL,12,Fas a "brutal and fatal attack on our
OL,13,Fbeloved wife, mother and granny, Bez
OL,14,FPurdy".
OL,16,FOn 27 March 2023, Parish left the
OL,17,Fmental health facility in Taunton and
OL,18,Ftravelled to the nearby village of
OL,19,FBroomfield, where he shaved his head
OL,20,Fand beard.
