OL,3,CMan escaped psychiatric unit before
OL,4,Ckilling 'beloved' churchwarden
OL,6,FHe entered Beryl Purdy's home, despite
OL,7,Fnot knowing the pensioner who was
OL,8,Flater pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,10,FParish was arrested the same evening
OL,11,Fwhilst walking along the verge of a
OL,12,Flocal road.
OL,14,FHe told the patrol officers he was
OL,15,Freturning home after a day at work on
OL,16,Fa nearby farm and gave a false name.
OL,18,FHe was initially sectioned to a secure
OL,19,Ffacility in Devon, but later released
OL,20,Finto custody and charged.
