OL,3,CMan escaped psychiatric unit before
OL,4,Ckilling 'beloved' churchwarden
OL,6,FAfter the sentencing, Beryl Purdy's
OL,7,Ffamily thanked the police and said:
OL,8,F"We are serving a life sentence of
OL,9,Ftorment knowing that we were unable to
OL,10,Fsave Bez from her attacker and the
OL,11,Foutcome of sentencing today also means
OL,12,Fthat her attacker avoids a life
OL,13,Fsentence.
OL,15,F"We would not wish our hell on any
OL,16,Fother family and urge for a review of
OL,17,Fhow the community can be protected
OL,18,Ffrom people with severe mental health
OL,19,Fissues."
