OL,6,FDI Debbie Hatch added: "This was a
OL,7,Fdeeply tragic incident in which Bez
OL,8,Flost her life in the most distressing
OL,9,Fof circumstances inside her own home.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts remain first and
OL,12,Fforemost with her family and friends,
OL,13,Fwho have shown great strength
OL,14,Fthroughout what has been an incredibly
OL,15,Fdifficult time.
