OL,3,CMan escaped psychiatric unit before
OL,4,Ckilling 'beloved' churchwarden
OL,6,F"This case highlights the complex
OL,7,Fintersection between mental health and
OL,8,Fcriminal justice. While the
OL,9,Fdefendant's illness does not excuse
OL,10,Fhis actions, it has been recognised as
OL,11,Fa key factor in the tragic events
OL,12,Fwhich unfolded.
OL,14,F"I want to commend the investigation
OL,15,Fteam, specialist medical professionals
OL,16,Fand Crown Prosecution Service for
OL,17,Ftheir diligence and professionalism
OL,18,Fthroughout this sensitive case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
