OL,6,F"Most importantly, I want to pay
OL,7,Ftribute to Bez and the life she led.
OL,8,FShe was described by those who knew
OL,9,Fher as an incredibly caring lady and
OL,10,Fbeloved by all who met her. Her death
OL,11,Fhas left a profound void in the lives
OL,12,Fof many, and we hope today's outcome
OL,13,Fprovides at least a degree of closure
OL,14,Fto those mourning her loss."
